Package: snakes-and-ladders
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0
Description: Accessible Snakes and Ladders is a simple yet delightful 
 implementation of the Snakes and Ladders game. The objective is to reach 100 
 before your opponents, while avoiding the treacherous snakes. The game is 
 inclusive, catering to both sighted players and those with visual impairments 
 who use screen reader.
 .
 Features five distinct game boards that can be played either in multiplayer
 mode or as a single player with a machine.
